```csharp
foreach (B b in myAs.OfType&lt;B&gt;()) {
    // do something
}
```

You need to iterate B instances in your A list. So, list A contains more than one type based on A. You have to filter list first and iterate or use IEnumerable.OfType(System.Linq namespace) method. 

    foreach (B b in myAs.OfType&lt;B&gt;())
